00:27:19.543 --> 00:27:20.627
- I came as a refugee.

503
00:27:20.710 --> 00:27:23.085
Lived here five years
and then became a citizen.

504
00:27:23.168 --> 00:27:25.126
My "childrens" are citizen.

505
00:27:25.210 --> 00:27:26.919
I'm very happy to live
in Sioux Falls

506
00:27:27.001 --> 00:27:30.627
because this is a very
nice place to raise family.

507
00:27:30.710 --> 00:27:31.960
- As you drive around.

508
00:27:32.043 --> 00:27:34.585
you'll see great diversity
in our small businesses.

509
00:27:34.669 --> 00:27:36.460
People that move in
to this community

510
00:27:36.543 --> 00:27:38.794
that start barbershops
or hair salons.

511
00:27:38.877 --> 00:27:42.543
grocery stores. restaurants.

512
00:27:42.627 --> 00:27:46.293
- I'm a refugee. I'm a Black.

513
00:27:46.377 --> 00:27:51.043
I'm originally from Somalia.
