514
00:27:51.126 --> 00:27:56.502
so which means I'm
a combination of four elements.

515
00:27:56.585 --> 00:27:58.335
I'm not a threat.

516
00:27:58.418 --> 00:28:00.335
- My gosh.
think of what they've overcome.

517
00:28:00.418 --> 00:28:03.126
especially refugees.
to get here.

518
00:28:03.210 --> 00:28:04.960
I don't know what we would be

519
00:28:05.043 --> 00:28:09.335
if we didn't have refugees
and immigrants in our country.

520
00:28:09.418 --> 00:28:11.126
- I wouldn't be here. for one.

521
00:28:11.210 --> 00:28:14.293
- 99% of the people living
in America

522
00:28:14.377 --> 00:28:16.460
are either immigrants
or refugees.

523
00:28:16.543 --> 00:28:19.710
The reason why America
is a great country now--

524
00:28:19.794 --> 00:28:24.710
it's because of people like me
and you and everyone.

525
00:29:00.669 --> 00:29:02.335
- When I say Sioux Falls.
South Dakota.

526
00:29:02.418 --> 00:29:04.085
people think
of Mount Rushmore.

527
00:29:04.168 --> 00:29:05.877
We are on the map
because of public art.

528
00:29:05.960 --> 00:29:08.043
because somebody carved
these four faces

529
00:29:08.126 --> 00:29:09.877
into the side of a mountain.

530
00:29:15.377 --> 00:29:18.919
- Most of my art comes from
just observation of nature

531
00:29:19.001 --> 00:29:23.418
and the "Arc of Dreams"
is a good example of that.

532
00:29:23.502 --> 00:29:26.251
In terms of the narrative
of the "Arc of Dreams."

533
00:29:26.335 --> 00:29:28.585
the idea is that
we have dreams

534
00:29:28.669 --> 00:29:30.752
that originate somewhere
in our consciousness

535
00:29:30.835 --> 00:29:33.710
and we can take 'em a certain
distance. but at some point.

536
00:29:33.794 --> 00:29:36.835
we have to trust ourselves
and the future.

537
00:29:36.919 --> 00:29:38.752
The synapse
between the two arcs

538
00:29:38.835 --> 00:29:41.293
represents that leap of faith.

539
00:29:44.335 --> 00:29:46.752
- Public art--it's
a significant component here

540
00:29:46.835 --> 00:29:47.960
in terms
of the quality of life.

541
00:29:48.043 --> 00:29:50.085
why people stay
and don't move away.

542
00:29:50.168 --> 00:29:51.919
And if they do move away
at a young age.

543
00:29:52.001 --> 00:29:53.085
they almost always come back

544
00:29:53.168 --> 00:29:54.960
because of the quality
of life.

545
00:30:07.627 --> 00:30:09.418
