568
00:31:07.043 --> 00:31:09.043
of what the opioid challenges

569
00:31:09.126 --> 00:31:10.794
that we face
in Sioux Falls are.

570
00:31:10.877 --> 00:31:12.627
I think we're very good
at hiding those things

571
00:31:12.710 --> 00:31:14.669
and not talking
about the problems.

572
00:31:14.752 --> 00:31:17.377
- We need to replace judgment
with compassion.

573
00:31:17.460 --> 00:31:19.919
