574
00:31:20.001 --> 00:31:22.210
- Angela's sharing
what she went through

575
00:31:22.293 --> 00:31:23.627
with her daughter.

576
00:31:23.710 --> 00:31:25.543
talking
about the opioid epidemic

577
00:31:25.627 --> 00:31:28.085
in the context of an illness.

578
00:31:28.168 --> 00:31:31.543
I think it's had a tremendous
impact far beyond Sioux Falls.

579
00:31:31.627 --> 00:31:33.377
probably far beyond
