Hugh French grew up
in Eastport.

1008
00:54:56.877 --> 00:54:58.585
Like people we've met
all over the country.

1009
00:54:58.669 --> 00:55:02.418
he moved away. then came home
to try to help his town.

1010
00:55:02.502 --> 00:55:04.251
He started the Tides Institute

1011
00:55:04.335 --> 00:55:07.043
with his wife.
Kristin McKinlay.

1012
00:55:07.126 --> 00:55:09.627
- We're committed
to this place.

1013
00:55:09.710 --> 00:55:12.085
That means collections.
exhibitions.

1014
00:55:12.168 --> 00:55:13.168
fostering new work.

1015
00:55:13.251 --> 00:55:15.960
getting involved
in the downtown heavily.

1016
00:55:16.043 --> 00:55:18.585
That's how you create change.

