1208
01:05:50.335 --> 01:05:51.502
- We do look for things

1209
01:05:51.585 --> 01:05:54.126
that people are struggling
with or achieving locally

1210
01:05:54.210 --> 01:05:56.919
that the national press
doesn't usually notice.

1211
01:06:04.627 --> 01:06:07.794
- The "Mountain Stage"!

1212
01:06:12.085 --> 01:06:13.752
- The West Side of Charleston

1213
01:06:13.835 --> 01:06:15.418
looks like what
you might expect

1214
01:06:15.502 --> 01:06:17.752
when you hear
about the city's troubles...

1215
01:06:19.377 --> 01:06:22.669
But every town is full
of things you don't expect.

1216
01:06:36.168 --> 01:06:38.502
- John and Tighe and
Ellen Bullock came up to me.

1217
01:06:38.585 --> 01:06:40.251
and I thought
they wanted me to paint

1218
01:06:40.335 --> 01:06:42.794
something on their building
like an advertisement.

1219
01:06:42.877 --> 01:06:44.335
And they said. "No. no.

1220
01:06:44.418 --> 01:06:46.335
"We want you to paint something
on the building

1221
01:06:46.418 --> 01:06:48.960
"that will change
the community.

1222
01:06:49.043 --> 01:06:52.210
change community.
change this whole place here."

1223
01:06:55.210 --> 01:06:59.126
