from the 34th Ohio Regiment.

1224
01:06:59.210 --> 01:07:00.835
They were stationed
right over here.

1225
01:07:00.919 --> 01:07:03.168
Painted some homeless people.

1226
01:07:03.251 --> 01:07:05.543
Her name was Froggy.
She passed away.

1227
01:07:05.627 --> 01:07:08.335
And Jim pushed her around.

1228
01:07:08.418 --> 01:07:10.502
She was a Navy veteran.

1229
01:07:10.585 --> 01:07:13.377
Natalie Tennant.
first female mountaineer.

1230
01:07:15.001 --> 01:07:16.502
Just various people came by.

1231
01:07:16.585 --> 01:07:18.669
Smitty would come by every day
and say.

1232
01:07:18.752 --> 01:07:20.335
"You got to put me in
with my dog.

1233
01:07:20.418 --> 01:07:22.168
You got to put me in there
with my dog."

1234
01:07:22.251 --> 01:07:23.502
I said. "Where's your dog?"

1235
01:07:23.585 --> 01:07:25.669
He said. "Oh. my dog's
been dead for ten years."

1236
01:07:25.752 --> 01:07:27.251
I said. "Oh. oh."

1237
01:07:31.251 --> 01:07:33.085
- I'm from a small coal town
in West Virginia

1238
01:07:33.168 --> 01:07:35.377
that had just become
dilapidated over the years.

1239
01:07:35.460 --> 01:07:38.377
and when I moved to Charleston
and I saw this neighborhood.

1240
01:07:38.460 --> 01:07:41.543
I thought. "Why is nothing
