01:18:49.418 --> 01:18:52.043
which always has this
really evocative sense to it.

1485
01:18:52.126 --> 01:18:53.418
the High Desert.

1486
01:18:56.835 --> 01:19:00.043
- Bend. Oregon. is the
culmination of this journey

1487
01:19:00.126 --> 01:19:04.418
because it's a town that found
its way back from failure.

1488
01:19:04.502 --> 01:19:06.710
- Bend was
a pretty depressed place.

1489
01:19:06.794 --> 01:19:08.210
Talking about the '80s

1490
01:19:08.293 --> 01:19:10.543
right after the logging boom
had sort of ended.

1491
01:19:10.627 --> 01:19:13.168
it was just sort of
a tough time.

1492
01:19:13.251 --> 01:19:15.835
- Bend was very much
a blue-collar town.

1493
01:19:15.919 --> 01:19:21.085
It has become a four-season
tourist destination.

1494
01:19:21.168 --> 01:19:24.085
- People had heard of it
being a vibrant community.

1495
01:19:24.168 --> 01:19:27.710
Next thing you know.
we're gonna move here.

1496
01:19:27.794 --> 01:19:30.293
- The people who've come
in the last ten years

1497
01:19:30.377 --> 01:19:34.210
don't understand
what it was like 30 years ago.

1498
01:19:34.293 --> 01:19:36.919
This was a small.
depressed timber town

1499
01:19:37.001 --> 01:19:40.085
that had to reach bottom.

1500
01:19:40.168 --> 01:19:42.001
But we were committed.

1501
01:19:50.669 --> 01:19:52.585
- I was an actress in LA.
and it was great.

1502
01:19:52.669 --> 01:19:55.085
But we wanted to raise
our family up here.

1503
01:19:55.168 --> 01:19:57.752
so I am actually gonna go back
to school

1504
01:19:57.835 --> 01:20:00.168
and get my master's
